      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:51:8",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/51/1040",
      "text": [
        " «لاَ إِلاَّ اَلصَّلاَةَ اَلَّتِي أَفَاقَ فِيهَا."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1040 - The Halabi asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-about a sick person who faints. Does he need to make up the prayers he missed during his fainting?\nImam (as) replied: \"No, except for the prayer in which he regained consciousness”."
        ]
      }
